@page "/"

<h2>Welcome to TitanHelp</h2>

<p class="lead">
    TitanHelp is a simple help desk ticket system. Create tickets for issues,
    set a priority, track status, and keep a record of problems and resolutions.
</p>

<div class="mt-3">
    <NavLink href="/tickets" class="btn btn-primary me-2">View All Tickets</NavLink>
    <NavLink href="/tickets/add" class="btn btn-success">Create a Ticket</NavLink>
</div>

<hr />

<h5>How it works</h5>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Add Ticket:</strong> Provide a name, description, priority and status.</li>
    <li><strong>All Tickets:</strong> Browse, view details, and edit existing tickets.</li>
    <li><strong>Status:</strong> Track progress with Open / InProgress / Resolved.</li>
</ul>
